706
00:29:09,706 --> 00:29:11,674
<i><b>And that's why
you can't go to the FBI.</b></i>

707
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,252
<i><b>There. Now you know.</b></i>

708
00:29:13,335 --> 00:29:17,215
<i><b>What I know is Rachel Zane
deserves to be in the Bar.</b></i>

709
00:29:17,339 --> 00:29:19,558
<i><b>So, you're not only
gonna stop blocking her,</b></i>

710
00:29:19,633 --> 00:29:22,227
<i><b>you're going to run interference
for her if someone else does.</b></i>

711
00:29:22,344 --> 00:29:24,221
<i><b>I don't have the power to do that.
Bullshit.</b></i>

712
00:29:24,304 --> 00:29:25,681
<i><b>You had the power to stop it.
You better believe</b></i>

713
00:29:25,764 --> 00:29:27,766
<i><b>that you can turn it
in the other direction.</b></i>

714
00:29:28,976 --> 00:29:30,978
<i><b>And in return,
you'll do what I want.</b></i>

715
00:29:31,395 --> 00:29:32,521
<i><b>No.</b></i>

