00:41:12,387 --> 00:41:13,639
<i><b>Yeah.</b></i>

978
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:28,870
<i><b>Louis, what...
What are you doing here?</b></i>

979
00:41:30,446 --> 00:41:32,289
<i><b>I needed to bring you
