980
00:41:33,324 --> 00:41:34,917
<i><b>What is all that?</b></i>

981
00:41:36,869 --> 00:41:38,371
<i><b>High school yearbooks,</b></i>

982
00:41:38,454 --> 00:41:41,458
<i><b>childhood photo albums, and six out
of seven of the highlight reels</b></i>

983
00:41:41,541 --> 00:41:43,589
<i><b>my mother shot of us
growing up.</b></i>

984
00:41:43,710 --> 00:41:46,429
<i><b>What happened to the seventh?
Oh.</b></i>

985
00:41:46,504 --> 00:41:48,131
<i><b>The Summer of D&D.</b></i>

986
00:41:48,423 --> 00:41:50,300
<i><b>And if it's
all the same to you,</b></i>

987
00:41:50,383 --> 00:41:52,263
<i><b>I would like to still be
able to have sex again.</b></i>

988
00:41:56,139 --> 00:41:57,516
<i><b>Louis.
