989
00:41:57,724 --> 00:41:59,647
<i><b>We don't know everything
about each other.</b></i>

990
00:42:00,309 --> 00:42:04,189
<i><b>But that just means we need to
get to know each other better.</b></i>

991
00:42:05,732 --> 00:42:07,029
<i><b>And what better way
to get to know each other</b></i>

992
00:42:07,108 --> 00:42:10,612
<i><b>than by preparing to bring
