996
00:42:21,789 --> 00:42:24,087
<i><b>Speaking of what
we went through today,</b></i>

997
00:42:24,834 --> 00:42:26,086
<i><b>how did it go?</b></i>

998
00:42:26,794 --> 00:42:30,640
<i><b>Why don't you take me home and
