1002
00:42:41,225 --> 00:42:42,693
<i><b>What about it?
Louis tried to lie to me.</b></i>

1003
00:42:42,769 --> 00:42:45,067
<i><b>He said it was
some sort of mix-up.</b></i>

1004
00:42:45,146 --> 00:42:47,444
<i><b>But when
I asked Donna about it,</b></i>

1005
00:42:47,523 --> 00:42:49,400
<i><b>she told me that
you were the one</b></i>

1006
00:42:49,484 --> 00:42:51,236
<i><b>who went to see
