1010
00:42:58,034 --> 00:43:00,378
<i><b>No. It was about leverage.</b></i>

1011
00:43:01,496 --> 00:43:02,918
<i><b>What do you mean?</b></i>

1012
00:43:02,997 --> 00:43:04,294
<i><b>The guy
